      "translation": "The Group's regulatory authority is the Insurance Authority of Hong Kong. The Group complies with solvency and capital adequacy requirements adopted by the Insurance Authority of Hong Kong. The Group's principal operating company is AIA Co., an insurance company registered in Hong Kong, which is required by the Insurance Authority of Hong Kong to comply with the solvency requirements under the Insurance Ordinance of Hong Kong."
